reviewText: The movie I bought was good, but there was one small point in which it tried to skip, thus why I'm only giving this a 4 star rather than a 5 star.

These three episodes are wonderful!  You get a good idea of the next season, watch action packed adventures, and so on.  If you're a Digimon fan and want to see some of the best Season 2 episodes, don't miss this.
